snippet.title: Jaleco Arcade 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Original Evercade handheld. This cart contains 8 arcade games from the Japanese developer, Jaleco. (Not to be confused with the Spanish arcade game developer, Gaelco)

Games in the cart:
00:07 - 64th. Street: A Detective Story
05:52 - Avenging Spirit
11:37 - Cybattler
16:33 - E.D.F. Earth Defense Force
20:27 - P-47: The Phantom Fighter
24:22 - Rod Land
33:07 - Saint Dragon
36:06 - The Astyanax
